PIES 0.0.0-SNAPSHOT Java Source Code Documentation

Base 
Package Description
com.gl.vn.me.ko.pies.base.config
Contains general API to work with configurations.
com.gl.vn.me.ko.pies.base.config.app
Contains Application-specific API to work with configurations.
com.gl.vn.me.ko.pies.base.constant
Contains Application-wide constants such as string resources, charset, locale and so on.
com.gl.vn.me.ko.pies.base.di
Contains API that together with GuiceLocator simplifies usage of dependency injection (DI) pattern.
com.gl.vn.me.ko.pies.base.doc
Contains annotations useful to document code.
com.gl.vn.me.ko.pies.base.feijoa
Contains various API and functionality.
com.gl.vn.me.ko.pies.base.main
Contains an entry point of the Application.
com.gl.vn.me.ko.pies.base.thread
Contains base Application thread classes and factories.
com.gl.vn.me.ko.pies.base.throwable
Contains base Application exception classes.
Platform 
Package Description
com.gl.vn.me.ko.pies.platform.app
Contains common platform functionality that is needed to implement App.
com.gl.vn.me.ko.pies.platform.client
Contains Client interface.
com.gl.vn.me.ko.pies.platform.client.tcp
Contains TCP implementation of the Client interface.
com.gl.vn.me.ko.pies.platform.server
Contains Server interface.
com.gl.vn.me.ko.pies.platform.server.rest
Contains REST extension of TcpServer.
com.gl.vn.me.ko.pies.platform.server.tcp
Contains TCP implementation of the Server interface.

Package Description
com.gl.vn.me.ko.pies.app.echo

com.gl.vn.me.ko.pies.app.initiator
Contains App logic for PIES Initiator Application.
com.gl.vn.me.ko.pies.app.proxy
Contains App logic for PIES Proxy Application.
